      <abstract>
        <p>A new Schiff base ether, <italic>p</italic>-<italic>n</italic>-(dimethylamino)benzylidene-<italic>p</italic>-dodecyloxyaniline, was synthesized and its IR, <sup>1</sup>H NMR, <sup>13</sup>C NMR and MS spectroscopic data are reported.</p>
      </abstract>
